c: 5
v: 69
t: "Zvirokwazvo, avo vanotenda (muhumwechete hwaAllah, mumutumwa wavo Muhammad (SAW) nezvose zvakave zvinodzikiswa kwaari kubva kuna Allah), neavo maJudha, maSabian nemaKristu, uyo anotenda muna Allah nezuva rekupedzisira, uye oshanda muhuchokwadi, kwavari kuchave kusina kutya kana kusuwa"